### Get Available Slots
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/appointments/available-slots?date=2023-10-01&serviceTypeId=cb986fdf-fb77-4a67-9001-6c303b364129

### Get Calendar View
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/appointments/calendar

### Create Appointment
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/appointments/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "f1365b8e-b091-4efd-897e-64a1382e17ca",
  "vehicleId": "2bc33d8f-a698-49d1-9b8e-883f39cb8cb8",
