### Cancel Appointment
DELETE http://localhost:4000/api/v1/appointments/123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000

### Update Appointment Status
PATCH http://localhost:4000/api/v1/appointments/6e3bc817-f492-4d9f-a842-28d4399e0143/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "CONFIRMED",
  "notes": "Appointment confirmed",
  "changedByStaffId": "3b7d25be-1886-43d7-b238-822cb448ff63",
